===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|ls=ic|宀|釆|田|t1=roof|t2=to distinguish}}. There are two theories about the component {{lang|zh|田}}. One is that it was originally {{zh-l|*口|mouth}}, then corrupted into {{zh-l|*曰|say}}, then further into {{lang|zh|田}}. The other one is that its a remnant from a variant form {{lang|zh|⿱宷思}} with {{lang|zh|心}} omitted. The {{w|Shuowen Jiezi}} describes {{lang|zh|審}} as the seal script variant of {{zh-l|*宷}}.

